#: ../../source/concepts/consensus-algorithm.rst:3
msgid "Consensus"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/concepts/consensus-algorithm.rst:5
msgid ""
"The consensus algorithm is the dynamic method through which nodes in a "
"blockchain system **reach an agreement** and **make decisions**."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/concepts/consensus-algorithm.rst:7
msgid ""
"|codename| utilizes an innovative mechanism called the **Proof-of-Stake "
"Plus** (PoS+), a modified version of the popular **Proof-of-Stake** "
"(|pos|) consensus."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/concepts/consensus-algorithm.rst:9
msgid ""
"In a basic **PoS** consensus algorithm, the formation of a new block in "
"the blockchain is stochastically assigned to a node based on a "
"combination of factors **related exclusively to the node owner's "
"wealth**."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/concepts/consensus-algorithm.rst:11
msgid ""
"The **PoS+** mechanism considers the account's stakes too, but it also "
"promotes the ecosystem's health by rewarding participants **based on "
"their activity**."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/concepts/consensus-algorithm.rst:17
msgid "Factors"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/concepts/consensus-algorithm.rst:19
msgid ""
"The algorithm considers the following factors when calculating an "
"account's **importance**, the measure that will ultimately be used to "
"choose the next harvesting node:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/concepts/consensus-algorithm.rst:21
msgid ""
"**Stake**: The total amount of :ref:`harvesting mosaic <harvesting-"
"mosaic>` held, since owners with larger balances have the incentive to "
"see the ecosystem flourish. Only accounts holding more than 10'000 "
"harvesting mosaics (**high-value accounts**) are :ref:`eligible "
"<account_eligibility>` for harvesting."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/concepts/consensus-algorithm.rst:22
msgid ""
"**Transactions**: The total amount of :doc:`fees <fees>` paid by an "
"account. This encourages being an active account in the network."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/concepts/consensus-algorithm.rst:23
msgid ""
"**Nodes**: The number of times an account has been the :ref:`beneficiary "
"<harvesting-rewards>` of the fees collected by a node. Thus the network "
"incentivizes accounts which run nodes."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/concepts/consensus-algorithm.rst:25
msgid ""
"Periodically, an **importance score** based on these three factors is "
"calculated for all high-value accounts. The importance score determines "
"an account's probability to :doc:`harvest <harvesting>` the next block."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/concepts/consensus-algorithm.rst:29
msgid "Partial scores"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/concepts/consensus-algorithm.rst:31
msgid ""
"The network calculates first the following **partial scores** for all "
"high-value accounts at the end of each importance period (720 blocks, "
"roughly 6 hours. See ``importanceGrouping`` in :ref:`config-network-"
"properties`):"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/concepts/consensus-algorithm.rst:33
msgid ""
"**Stake Score** (:math:`S`): Account's balance divided by the balance of "
"all high value accounts, at the end of the period."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/concepts/consensus-algorithm.rst:34
msgid ""
"**Transaction Score** (:math:`T`): Total amount of fees paid by the "
"account divided by the total amount of fees paid by all high value "
"accounts during the period."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/concepts/consensus-algorithm.rst:35
msgid ""
"**Node Score** (:math:`N`): Number of times the account has been the "
":ref:`beneficiary <harvesting-rewards>` of a node fee divided by the "
"number of times all high value accounts have been the beneficiary of a "
"node fee, during the period."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/concepts/consensus-algorithm.rst:36
msgid ""
"**Activity Score** (:math:`A`): Average of the :math:`T` and :math:`N` "
"scores weighted **80%** and **20%** respectively, divided by the "
"account's balance. Dividing by the account's balance gives some boost to "
"small accounts, because their importance score will depend more on their "
"activity and less on their stake."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/concepts/consensus-algorithm.rst:38
msgid "An absolute activity score (:math:`A'`) is calculated first:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/concepts/consensus-algorithm.rst:40
msgid "A' = \\frac{10000}{Balance}(0.8T+0.2N)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/concepts/consensus-algorithm.rst:44
msgid ""
"And the actual activity score (:math:`A`) is calculated by dividing "
":math:`A'` by the sum of the absolute activity scores of all high value "
"accounts."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/concepts/consensus-algorithm.rst:46
msgid "The importance score is then calculated based on the above partial scores."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/concepts/consensus-algorithm.rst:50
msgid "Importance score"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/concepts/consensus-algorithm.rst:52
msgid ""
"The importance score :math:`I` is calculated as the average of the "
":math:`S` and :math:`A` scores, weighted by an activity factor "
":math:`\\gamma`:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/concepts/consensus-algorithm.rst:54
msgid "I = \\gamma A + (1-\\gamma)S"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/concepts/consensus-algorithm.rst:58
msgid "In the |codename| network :math:`\\gamma` is 0.05 (**5%**)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/concepts/consensus-algorithm.rst:60
msgid ""
"Finally, among all accounts :ref:`eligible for harvesting "
"<account_eligibility>`, the probability that a particular one is chosen "
"is proportional to its **effective importance score**, which is defined "
"as **the smaller of the previous two importance scores** :math:`I`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/concepts/consensus-algorithm.rst:64
msgid ""
"Since scores are calculated every 720 blocks (roughly 6 hours) and the "
"smaller of the previous **two scores** is used when calculating "
"harvesting probabilities, when you first fund an account it will require "
"**12 hours** to have a probability greater than zero."
msgstr ""

